<h1>Math()</h1>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.PI</h2>

<p>Math.PI returns the ratio of a circle's circumference to its diameter:</p>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = Math.PI;
</script>

</body>
</html>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.round()</h2>

<p>Math.round(x) returns the value of x rounded to its nearest integer:</p>

<p id="good"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("good").innerHTML = Math.round(4.6);
</script>

</body>
</html>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.ceil()</h2>

<p>Math.ceil() rounds a number <strong>up</strong> to its nearest integer:</p>

<p id="jim"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("jim").innerHTML = Math.ceil(2.8);
</script>

</body>
</html>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.floor()</h2>

<p>Math.floor(x) returns the value of x rounded <strong>down</strong> to its nearest integer:</p>

<p id="lp"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("lp").innerHTML = Math.floor(4.2);
</script>

</body>
</html>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.trunc()</h2>

<p>Math.trunc(x) returns the integer part of x:</p>

<p id="nm"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("nm").innerHTML = Math.trunc(2.1);
</script>

</body>
</html>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.sign()</h2>

<p>Math.sign(x) returns if x is negative, null or positive:</p>

<p id="uh"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("uh").innerHTML = Math.sign(2.8);
</script>

</body>
</html>

<h1>Random</h1>
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.random()</h2>

<p>Math.random() returns a random number between 0 (included) and 1 (excluded):</p>

<p id="king"></p>

<script>
document.getElementById("king").innerHTML = Math.random();
</script>

</body>
</html>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h2>JavaScript Math.random() with floor</h2>

<p>Every time you click the button, getRndInteger(min, max) returns a random number between 0 
and 9 (both included):</p>

<button onclick="document.getElementById('ko').innerHTML = getRndInteger(0,10)">Click Me</button>

<p id="ko"></p>

<script>
function getRndInteger(min, max) {
  return Math.floor(Math.random() * (max - min)) + min;
}
</script>

</body>
</html>




